{"tid":1456703,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我屌你老母連登仔同現場叫人撤果班","createTime":"2019-08-12T10:38:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T10:56:37.000Z","uid":10628,"like":13,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"7fcd936b5481b61e4e5c284995d1dd8d1c8d4837","tid":1456703,"uid":10628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:38:40.000Z","msg":"琴晚個女義士俾黑警射爆隻眼，多名義士被捕，全城憤慨，即刻吹雞今日入機場，諗住同港共政權玩鋪show hand。<br />\n<br />\n黎到果陣完全估唔撚到咁多人，好撚感動，覺得香港食粥食飯靠呢鋪，點撚知唔夠5點，去左廁所收一陣電話，返到黎唔見左一半！係一半！乜撚野事！？竟然現場有人叫撤，仲好撚多人跟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我真係好撚失望，咁撚多人驚閪咩！？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢點會夠膽係咁多人情況下（當中不乏旅客）放彈！估唔到俾人帶少少風向就不攻自破！點撚樣對得住被捕同埋受傷既義士！？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n成場運動最撚關鍵既一個據點會咁易咁快散，好撚灰心！<br />\n我相信唔會再有下次可以有咁既動員力<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n再一次屌撚晒你地老母！"},{"pid":"80c06516cc0fbafcf08db61113c2dac20c51f8cb","tid":1456703,"uid":10628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:44:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"453c23ad0fd7cf9d70dac896a30f81f1555fbdaa","tid":1456703,"uid":10628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:44:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dafa984372a8ff9b883bfc73b9fa762a506834f2","tid":1456703,"uid":10628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:44:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60096d0d81ad03539a61e2ca0f6a025dc8bd1819","tid":1456703,"uid":23340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:45:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d875c5fd4c826a2ddaf086cb1cd626e91ecfba8d","tid":1456703,"uid":10628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:45:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60f945ac6a7a9a2ba3d51ad574db00bd58b387e2","tid":1456703,"uid":10628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:45:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19b15a9c4c35c700b8a564a6a394bb2135964c8c","tid":1456703,"uid":10628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:45:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8f36623499ebdfaec1b9230f63e3ba45ba89635","tid":1456703,"uid":271617,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:46:14.000Z","msg":"By：黃之峰 facebook 現場 18:17<br />\n<br />\n目前我人仍在機埸，明白大家對於近日的抗議有一定憂慮，但實在無需過分恐慌，一些假消息傳出去也是不必要的。<br />\n<br />\n一、<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">#香港機場沒有切斷任何網絡</span></span>，順粹是人群聚集後網絡收得很差而已，過去遊行人數多的時候也有同樣狀況。<br />\n<br />\n二、目前機場燈火通明，機場快綫及機場巴士仍正常運作，有推着行李的香港人仍然繼續前往機場，亦有示威者正在陸續離開，包括沿機場路步行至東涌。<br />\n<br />\n三、客運大樓的大部份商店已落閘，現場所見仍有過千名示威者於接機大堂。<br />\n<br />\n四、目前仍有班機等待抵港，包括夜晚8:30的班機，亦有班機等待飛離香港。"},{"pid":"a1ba9f65fe6aef1a60cd4550ccf92fcfbce9c8fa","tid":1456703,"uid":99418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:46:36.000Z","msg":"長做長有<br />\n今日完左唔係代表完"},{"pid":"f65ccced6cef81443544eee23416146ea22b6d08","tid":1456703,"uid":305408,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:46:46.000Z","msg":"真<br />\n人地擺幾隻兵 就嚇走幾萬人"},{"pid":"277f63ecd48ef8c4c0beed16771ea01e5820e25e","tid":1456703,"uid":236073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:46:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2917610204ac56db03305be52aa4e43b25e2475b","tid":1456703,"uid":265134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:47:57.000Z","msg":"幾時都係<br />\n人多就唔驚<br />\n走根本就係害死走得慢嘅人<br />\n機場唔可以用硬攻<br />\n佢就同你玩心理戰<br />\n結果香港人輸晒"},{"pid":"12b63edc8cb415bbd8bd71d99430c4352fcd027f","tid":1456703,"uid":128178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:48:04.000Z","msg":"尾班車最保守都走一半人<br />\n唔再出來既人一樣唔會再出<br />\n到尾班先走 到時拉人風險大升"},{"pid":"1d55356ca78def6eb44d1959475ad7f04b9a8792","tid":1456703,"uid":63452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:48:34.000Z","msg":"琴日mtr 站咪照放<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋都癱瘓左機場，留守有咩用? Be water be  撚左去邊?"},{"pid":"2468c82d0f25d02db3ba2797c3b36d4492938492","tid":1456703,"uid":236073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:49:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7b35710c7938a111b8b86c5020c9d3017bc68ed9","tid":1456703,"uid":296928,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:51:31.000Z","msg":"又話還眼，屌我老母都係咁講。停機講撚到64咁撚樣。<br />\n仲記唔記得民間記者會講過，解放軍入黎先返屋企訓。<br />\n咁撚多多人入緊黎，俾班鬼過散水，就散水。目標已達？8.12還眼，還你地老母阿！ 要團結阿。出個通告就散水，出黎做咩撚野阿。<br />\n散唔撚緊要，東涌等，一話飛得唔該圍佢老母。"},{"pid":"4f9a756f79f3f01afb8beb1aa1608f4a311d575a","tid":1456703,"uid":54181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:54:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"69fc56cd7b1535e40f9628146bb1d87dc9ae8a8f","tid":1456703,"uid":266938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:56:37.000Z","msg":"咁真係冇旅客俾你宣傳<br />\n咁高風險用黎自己圍爐搏乜？<br />\n如果依家係有幾個人俾人爆左頭你會唔會咁講？"}]}